{"tid":2007844,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"瑞典街頭出現「蝙蝠俠習近平」惡搞海報","createTime":"2020-05-08T14:50:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T17:53:03.000Z","uid":28765,"like":125,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"ff98d687915463206aaadf195a5b739976a4db89","tid":2007844,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:50:27.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒疾病，COVID-19）疫情衝擊全球，目前全球確診人數共385萬9559例，死亡逾26萬人，日前許多國家表態，要向中國政府究責，並找出病毒源頭，近日瑞典街頭出現多張以「習近平」和「蝙蝠俠」為主題的海報，諷刺意味滿點。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/05/08/phpys5TFz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F05%2F08%2Fphpys5TFz.jpg&h=0e6956f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2020/05/08/phpr6cz0g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2020%2F05%2F08%2Fphpr6cz0g.jpg&h=e4f89316&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n瑞典街頭出現以習近平為主題的海報。（美聯社<br />\n<br />\n武漢P4實驗室研究人員早期未著防護服進行蝙蝠實驗的照片，成為新型冠狀病毒來源的討論焦點。近日瑞典街頭出現多幅海報，海報中將習近平畫上突出的雙耳，下方寫上大大的「蝙蝠俠」，其中「蝙蝠」二字還特意以顏色另做區分，具有濃厚的諷刺意味。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體報導，今年2月，香港銅鑼灣書店的瑞典籍股東桂民海因「為境外非法提供情報」罪，被中國判處10年有期徒刑，加上先前中國官媒抨擊瑞典因應武漢肺炎防疫措施，4月瑞典除了解除與上海姊妹市關係，也宣布關閉最後一所孔子課堂（Confucius Classroom），種種跡象都被外界認為中瑞友誼惡化。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3159528\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3159528&d=ZKl1Acg0IOD8KmAOqHMUQB0Z1crOiE0eyIPSb4MeDzY%3D&h=d6cae425\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3159528&h=cce5eb7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3159528</a>"},{"pid":"4570e3860596fd838ccb8684e4056b551fcd8f89","tid":2007844,"uid":51271,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T14:51:01.000Z","msg":"好撚靚呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class